Name: The Complex: Found Footage
About the game: Experience the liminal world of the backrooms through a VHS camera, immersing into a mysterious story and wandering the dream-like structures... Might there be something following you? The Complex: Found Footage is a walking simulator with the world being viewed through a VHS camera. Uncover a mystery that lies in the world of 'The Complex', though it may leave more questions rather than answers... • Traverse and explore the huge, unforgiving and mysterious world. • Deal with an unknown entity. This game is not connected with Kane Pixels' Backrooms. Also not recommended for lower end systems. -W,A,S,D to move -Left Shift to sprint -Left CTRL to crouch -F to toggle flashlight
